metadata.name: The dwarf
metadata.description:
Dwarf made with graphite, which allows to show a hyperrealism in the strokes and details.

They are those fictitious and not so fictitious people who over time have become more visible in society.

By the other hand they have shown us their great strength and power to overcome all injustices and adversities.

Their inherent qualities are their loyalty, courage and honesty. 

Size: 7008 x 9912
